<div class="container-fluid stories">
    <h3>Latest Success Stories</h3>
    <p>Learn more about how to use MVTec software products to develop high-innovative solutions: Read here the
        newest stories.
        <br> MVTec technologies are used in many different industries worldwide. To find a reference story out of
        your branch, please take a look at our success story page.
    </p>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-lg-4">
            <a class="story" href="#">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="<%= stories[0].image %>" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <ul class="nav">
                            <% for( let index = 0; index < stories[0].tag.length; index++ ) { %>
                                <li><%= stories[0].tag[index] %></li>
                            <% } %>
                        </ul>
                        <h4><%= stories[0].title %></h4>
                        <div>
                            <p class="card-text"
                                style="white-space: nowrap;overflow: hidden !important;text-overflow: ellipsis;">
                                <%= stories[0].description %>    </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-lg-4">
            <a class="story" href="#">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="<%= stories[1].image %>" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
